Package com.github.alinaioanaflorea.xmldiff.ui.swing.eventhandlers

This package holds the GUI's event handlers

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CleanUpActionListener
    This class cleans the files generated by XmlDiff on the user's machine
    CloseAppListeners
    This class holds the Listeners that close all the opened XmlDiff windows
    ExitWindowListener
    This class opens a new window which gives the user the option to clean the files generated by XmlDiff on his/her machine
    FieldListeners
    This class holds the field listeners that provide help on how to set the value of a fields in the XmlDiff's main GUI
    InputButtonActionListener
    This class facilitates the searching and opening of a file from the user's machine
    NewWindowMouseListener
    This class opens a new windows to display the XmlDiff's output, log or documentation data.
    ProcessButtonActionListener
    This class validates the input file paths and triggers the output generation, while updating the gui's state messages
    ResetButtonActionListener
    This class resets the content of the GUI field that holds the path to the configuration file
